{
  "name": "Progress Indicator",
  "tier": "02_components",
  "key": "progress",
  "type": "atom",
  "description": "A component for visually communicating the status of a process, loading, or progress.",
  "guidelines": {
    "purpose": "Progress Indicator visually communicates processing, loading, or progress status to the user. Circle type is used for indeterminate processes (loading), while Bar type is used for definite progress values.",
    "types": {
      "Circle (Spinner)": "A 3/4 arc drawn with a gradient and a continuous rotation animation. Used when the completion time of a process is unknown.",
      "Bar (Progress Bar)": "Expresses the progress percentage (0-100%) through width. Used when the completion can be predicted."
    },
    "style": {
      "circle_size": {
        "small": "20xvar(--sizing-500)",
        "medium": "32xvar(--sizing-800)",
        "large": "40xvar(--sizing-1000)"
      },
      "bar_specs": {
        "track_color": "var(--color-background-tertiary)",
        "fill_color": "System Gradient"
      }
    },
    "usage_guidelines": [
      "Display Progress Indicator when a process takes 2 seconds or longer. Do not use for short processes.",
      "Circle type is suitable for compact spaces like within buttons, inline, or full-screen overlays. Select the size based on the display context.",
      "Bar type is used for file uploads, downloads, or step-by-step progress where the percentage can be retrieved Numerically.",
      "Providing text such as 'Processing...' along with the Indicator improves the user's waiting experience."
    ],
    "do_dont": {
      "do": [
        "Communicate context by combining with processing text."
      ],
      "dont": [
        "Do not align multiple spinners on the same screen. Express processing as a single unit."
      ]
    },
    "_rawHtml": "\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Guide</h2>\n        <div class=\"guide-card\">\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Purpose</h3>\n            <p>Progress Indicatorは、処理・読み込み・進捗状況をユーザーに視覚的に伝えるコンポーネントです。Circleタイプは不確定な処理（ローディング）に、Barタイプは確定した進捗値の表示に使用します。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Type</h3>\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\">Circle（スピナー）</h4>\n            <p>3/4 の弧がグラデーションで描かれ、連続回転アニメーションにより処理中の状態を表現します。処理の完了時刻が不明な場合に使用します。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-600);align-items:center;margin-top:var(--spacing-300);\">\n              <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--small\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-600);height:var(--sizing-600);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-g-sm\" x1=\"4.631\" y1=\"17.096\" x2=\"19.189\" y2=\"5.501\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M4.49612 16.1716C4.09991 15.818 4.06536 15.2102 4.41895 14.8139C4.77254 14.4177 5.38037 14.3832 5.77658 14.7368C6.93168 15.7676 8.41969 16.3463 10.0002 16.3463C13.5051 16.3463 16.3464 13.5051 16.3464 10.0002C16.3464 6.4953 13.5051 3.65403 10.0002 3.65403C9.4692 3.65403 9.03871 3.22354 9.03871 2.6925C9.03871 2.16145 9.4692 1.73096 10.0002 1.73096C14.5672 1.73096 18.2695 5.43322 18.2695 10.0002C18.2695 14.5672 14.5672 18.2694 10.0002 18.2694C7.94279 18.2694 6.00028 17.5139 4.49612 16.1716Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-g-sm)\"/></svg></div><div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--medium\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-800);height:var(--sizing-800);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-g-md\" x1=\"7.410\" y1=\"27.354\" x2=\"30.702\" y2=\"8.802\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M7.1938 25.8745C6.55986 25.3088 6.50458 24.3362 7.07033 23.7023C7.63607 23.0684 8.6086 23.0131 9.24253 23.5788C11.0907 25.2282 13.4715 26.1541 16.0004 26.1541C21.6082 26.1541 26.1542 21.6081 26.1542 16.0003C26.1542 10.3925 21.6082 5.84645 16.0004 5.84645C15.1507 5.84645 14.4619 5.15766 14.4619 4.30799C14.4619 3.45832 15.1507 2.76953 16.0004 2.76953C23.3075 2.76953 29.2312 8.69315 29.2312 16.0003C29.2312 23.3075 23.3075 29.2311 16.0004 29.2311C12.7085 29.2311 9.60045 28.0223 7.1938 25.8745Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-g-md)\"/></svg></div><div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--large\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-1000);height:var(--sizing-1000);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-g-lg\" x1=\"9.262\" y1=\"34.192\" x2=\"38.378\" y2=\"11.003\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M8.99225 32.3431C8.19983 31.636 8.13073 30.4203 8.83791 29.6279C9.54509 28.8355 10.7607 28.7664 11.5532 29.4735C13.8634 31.5352 16.8394 32.6927 20.0005 32.6927C27.0103 32.6927 32.6928 27.0101 32.6928 20.0004C32.6928 12.9906 27.0103 7.30807 20.0005 7.30807C18.9384 7.30807 18.0774 6.44708 18.0774 5.38499C18.0774 4.3229 18.9384 3.46191 20.0005 3.46191C29.1344 3.46191 36.539 10.8664 36.539 20.0004C36.539 29.1343 29.1344 36.5388 20.0005 36.5388C15.8856 36.5388 12.0006 35.0279 8.99225 32.3431Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-g-lg)\"/></svg></div>\n            </div>\n\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\" style=\"margin-top:var(--sizing-500);\">Bar（プログレスバー）</h4>\n            <p>進捗の割合（0〜100%）を横幅で表現します。処理の完了予測が可能な場合に使用します。トラック色は <code style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;background: var(--color-background-secondary);padding:var(--border-width-100) var(--space-xxs);border-radius:var(--border-width-300);\">var(--color-background-tertiary)</code>、フィル色はシステムグラデーション。</p>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:var(--spacing-300);max-width:calc(var(--sizing-100) * 80);\">\n              <div class=\"progress-bar\" style=\"width:calc(var(--sizing-100) * 70);\"><div class=\"progress-bar-fill\" style=\"width:40%;\"></div></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Style — Size (Circle)</h3>\n            <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:var(--spacing-400);max-width:calc(var(--sizing-100) * 70);margin-top:var(--spacing-200);\">\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--small\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-600);height:var(--sizing-600);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-gs-sm\" x1=\"4.631\" y1=\"17.096\" x2=\"19.189\" y2=\"5.501\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M4.49612 16.1716C4.09991 15.818 4.06536 15.2102 4.41895 14.8139C4.77254 14.4177 5.38037 14.3832 5.77658 14.7368C6.93168 15.7676 8.41969 16.3463 10.0002 16.3463C13.5051 16.3463 16.3464 13.5051 16.3464 10.0002C16.3464 6.4953 13.5051 3.65403 10.0002 3.65403C9.4692 3.65403 9.03871 3.22354 9.03871 2.6925C9.03871 2.16145 9.4692 1.73096 10.0002 1.73096C14.5672 1.73096 18.2695 5.43322 18.2695 10.0002C18.2695 14.5672 14.5672 18.2694 10.0002 18.2694C7.94279 18.2694 6.00028 17.5139 4.49612 16.1716Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-gs-sm)\"/></svg></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color:var(--color-content-tertiary);\">small<br><span style=\"color: var(--color-content-tertiary);font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;\">20×var(--sizing-500)</span></span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--medium\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-800);height:var(--sizing-800);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-gs-md\" x1=\"7.410\" y1=\"27.354\" x2=\"30.702\" y2=\"8.802\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M7.1938 25.8745C6.55986 25.3088 6.50458 24.3362 7.07033 23.7023C7.63607 23.0684 8.6086 23.0131 9.24253 23.5788C11.0907 25.2282 13.4715 26.1541 16.0004 26.1541C21.6082 26.1541 26.1542 21.6081 26.1542 16.0003C26.1542 10.3925 21.6082 5.84645 16.0004 5.84645C15.1507 5.84645 14.4619 5.15766 14.4619 4.30799C14.4619 3.45832 15.1507 2.76953 16.0004 2.76953C23.3075 2.76953 29.2312 8.69315 29.2312 16.0003C29.2312 23.3075 23.3075 29.2311 16.0004 29.2311C12.7085 29.2311 9.60045 28.0223 7.1938 25.8745Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-gs-md)\"/></svg></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color:var(--color-content-tertiary);\">medium<br><span style=\"color: var(--color-content-tertiary);font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;\">32×var(--sizing-800)</span></span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--large\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-1000);height:var(--sizing-1000);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-gs-lg\" x1=\"9.262\" y1=\"34.192\" x2=\"38.378\" y2=\"11.003\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M8.99225 32.3431C8.19983 31.636 8.13073 30.4203 8.83791 29.6279C9.54509 28.8355 10.7607 28.7664 11.5532 29.4735C13.8634 31.5352 16.8394 32.6927 20.0005 32.6927C27.0103 32.6927 32.6928 27.0101 32.6928 20.0004C32.6928 12.9906 27.0103 7.30807 20.0005 7.30807C18.9384 7.30807 18.0774 6.44708 18.0774 5.38499C18.0774 4.3229 18.9384 3.46191 20.0005 3.46191C29.1344 3.46191 36.539 10.8664 36.539 20.0004C36.539 29.1343 29.1344 36.5388 20.0005 36.5388C15.8856 36.5388 12.0006 35.0279 8.99225 32.3431Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-gs-lg)\"/></svg></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color:var(--color-content-tertiary);\">large<br><span style=\"color: var(--color-content-tertiary);font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;\">40×var(--sizing-1000)</span></span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Usage Guidelines</h3>\n            <ul class=\"guide-list\">\n              <li>処理時間が2秒以上かかる場合にProgress Indicatorを表示します。短い処理には使用しないでください。</li>\n              <li>Circleタイプはボタン内・インライン・全画面オーバーレイなど、コンパクトなスペースでの使用に適しています。サイズは表示コンテキストに合わせて選択します。</li>\n              <li>Barタイプはファイルアップロード・ダウンロード・ステップ進捗など、進捗割合が数値で取得できる場面で使用します。</li>\n              <li>Progress Indicatorと合わせて「処理中です」などのテキストを表示すると、ユーザーの待機体験が向上します。</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Do &amp; Don't</h3>\n            <div class=\"do-dont-grid\">\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header do\">✓ Do</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\" style=\"flex-direction:column;gap:var(--spacing-300);align-items:flex-start;\">\n                  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-lg);\">\n                    <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--medium\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-800);height:var(--sizing-800);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-dd-do\" x1=\"7.410\" y1=\"27.354\" x2=\"30.702\" y2=\"8.802\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M7.1938 25.8745C6.55986 25.3088 6.50458 24.3362 7.07033 23.7023C7.63607 23.0684 8.6086 23.0131 9.24253 23.5788C11.0907 25.2282 13.4715 26.1541 16.0004 26.1541C21.6082 26.1541 26.1542 21.6081 26.1542 16.0003C26.1542 10.3925 21.6082 5.84645 16.0004 5.84645C15.1507 5.84645 14.4619 5.15766 14.4619 4.30799C14.4619 3.45832 15.1507 2.76953 16.0004 2.76953C23.3075 2.76953 29.2312 8.69315 29.2312 16.0003C29.2312 23.3075 23.3075 29.2311 16.0004 29.2311C12.7085 29.2311 9.60045 28.0223 7.1938 25.8745Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-dd-do)\"/></svg></div>\n                    <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color:var(--color-content-tertiary);\">データを読み込んでいます...</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">処理中のテキストと組み合わせてコンテキストを伝える。</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header dont\">✕ Don't</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\" style=\"flex-direction:row;gap:var(--spacing-300);align-items:center;opacity:0.6;\">\n                  <div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--small\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-600);height:var(--sizing-600);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-dd-dn1\" x1=\"4.631\" y1=\"17.096\" x2=\"19.189\" y2=\"5.501\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M4.49612 16.1716C4.09991 15.818 4.06536 15.2102 4.41895 14.8139C4.77254 14.4177 5.38037 14.3832 5.77658 14.7368C6.93168 15.7676 8.41969 16.3463 10.0002 16.3463C13.5051 16.3463 16.3464 13.5051 16.3464 10.0002C16.3464 6.4953 13.5051 3.65403 10.0002 3.65403C9.4692 3.65403 9.03871 3.22354 9.03871 2.6925C9.03871 2.16145 9.4692 1.73096 10.0002 1.73096C14.5672 1.73096 18.2695 5.43322 18.2695 10.0002C18.2695 14.5672 14.5672 18.2694 10.0002 18.2694C7.94279 18.2694 6.00028 17.5139 4.49612 16.1716Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-dd-dn1)\"/></svg></div><div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--small\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-600);height:var(--sizing-600);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-dd-dn2\" x1=\"4.631\" y1=\"17.096\" x2=\"19.189\" y2=\"5.501\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M4.49612 16.1716C4.09991 15.818 4.06536 15.2102 4.41895 14.8139C4.77254 14.4177 5.38037 14.3832 5.77658 14.7368C6.93168 15.7676 8.41969 16.3463 10.0002 16.3463C13.5051 16.3463 16.3464 13.5051 16.3464 10.0002C16.3464 6.4953 13.5051 3.65403 10.0002 3.65403C9.4692 3.65403 9.03871 3.22354 9.03871 2.6925C9.03871 2.16145 9.4692 1.73096 10.0002 1.73096C14.5672 1.73096 18.2695 5.43322 18.2695 10.0002C18.2695 14.5672 14.5672 18.2694 10.0002 18.2694C7.94279 18.2694 6.00028 17.5139 4.49612 16.1716Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-dd-dn2)\"/></svg></div><div class=\"progress-circle progress-circle--small\" style=\"width:var(--sizing-600);height:var(--sizing-600);\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"pgc-dd-dn3\" x1=\"4.631\" y1=\"17.096\" x2=\"19.189\" y2=\"5.501\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1)\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"/></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M4.49612 16.1716C4.09991 15.818 4.06536 15.2102 4.41895 14.8139C4.77254 14.4177 5.38037 14.3832 5.77658 14.7368C6.93168 15.7676 8.41969 16.3463 10.0002 16.3463C13.5051 16.3463 16.3464 13.5051 16.3464 10.0002C16.3464 6.4953 13.5051 3.65403 10.0002 3.65403C9.4692 3.65403 9.03871 3.22354 9.03871 2.6925C9.03871 2.16145 9.4692 1.73096 10.0002 1.73096C14.5672 1.73096 18.2695 5.43322 18.2695 10.0002C18.2695 14.5672 14.5672 18.2694 10.0002 18.2694C7.94279 18.2694 6.00028 17.5139 4.49612 16.1716Z\" fill=\"url(#pgc-dd-dn3)\"/></svg></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">同一画面に複数のスピナーを並べない。処理はまとめて1つで表現する。</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n    "
  },
  "selector": ".progress-circle, .progress-bar"
}